eshop.entity

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • eshop.entity.Item

  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    Item class models a stock item in eShop program. Items can be interactively produced using eshop.parser.Parser#inputItem() factory method
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Trayan Iliev, http://iproduct.org
    See Also:
    Parser
